### Obtener todas las órdenes de compra
GET http://localhost:3003/sales/purchased-orders HTTP/1.1

### Obtener orden de compra por ID
GET http://localhost:3003/sales/purchased-orders/id/1 HTTP/1.1


### Obtener orden de compra por ID
GET http://localhost:3003/sales/purchased-orders/like/+52 HTTP/1.1

### Obtener orden de compra por código de orden
GET http://localhost:3003/sales/purchased-orders/code/ORD123 HTTP/1.1

### Obtener órdenes de compra por cliente
GET http://localhost:3003/sales/purchased-orders/client/1 HTTP/1.1

### Crear una nueva orden de compra
POST http://localhost:3003/sales/purchased-orders HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "order_code": "ORsadssaD12ddfd34556",
    "delivery_date": "2025-05-02T00:00:00Z",
    "status": "Pending",
    "client_id": 2,
    "client_address_id": 2,
    "total_price": 320.00
}


### Actualizar una orden de compra
PATCH http://localhost:3003/sales/purchased-orders/7 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "shipped"
}

### Eliminar una orden de compra
DELETE http://localhost:3003/sales/purchased-orders/7 HTTP/1.1

